{c_label}Cooldown: {/c}{c_resource}{Cooldown Time}{/c} seconds
Aldkin emits {c_number}{SF_0}{/c} ghostly souls at enemies, each {c_important}Haunting{/c} their victims and dealing {c_number}{dot:HAUNT_BUFF}{/c} Shadow damage over {c_number}{buffduration:HAUNT_BUFF}{/c} seconds. If a target dies while being {c_important}Haunted{/c}, its soul jumps to another target.

Aldkin's Mercenary Core Skill alters his {c_important}Fate{/c} and Basic Attack.
{c_label}Fate:{/c} {c_important}Foredoomed{/c}
{c_label}Basic Attack:{/c} {c_important}Shadow Strike{/c}
Aldkin shoots a burst of dark bolts at an enemy, dealing {c_number}{payload:MELEE_PAYLOAD_TOOLTIP}{/c} Shadow damage.
